    <div class="wrapper">
      <div class="Grid Grid--gutters Grid--full Grid--gutter">
        <div class="Grid-cell">
          <div class="element">
            <h1 class="fontWeight400">Problem</h1>
            <h4>Checkout is treated as a final step, but user behavior remains non-linear and decision-driven. Users continue adjusting key inputs during checkout, while the system assumes a stable, ready-to-complete state—leading to friction, confusion, and drop-off.</h4>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="wrapper">
      <div class="Grid Grid--gutters Grid--full Grid--gutter">
        <div class="Grid-cell">
