        <div class="Grid Grid--gutters Grid--cols-2 Grid--top accTrigger">
          <div class="Grid-cell">
            <div class="element">
              <h4 class="fontWeight400">Largest drop-off occurs before checkout begins</h4>
              <h6>The largest drop-off occurs before checkout begins, particularly on mobile, where over 60% of users abandon after adding items to cart.</h6>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="align-right">
            <div class="element">
              <div class="accIcon iconAccTrigger"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accContent" style="">
          <div class="Grid Grid--gutters Grid--full Grid--gutter">
            <div class="Grid-cell">
              <div class="element">
                <h6>Funnel: add_to_cart → begin_checkout</h6>
                <h6><span class="fontWeight400"> Web: </span>~49% continue</h6>
                <h6><span class="fontWeight400"> Mobile web:</span> ~34% continue </h6>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="spacingSmall"></div>

        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="accItem">
        <div class="Grid Grid--gutters Grid--cols-2 Grid--top accTrigger">
          <div class="Grid-cell">
            <div class="element">
              <h4 class="fontWeight400">Post-checkout entry completion is high</h4>
              <h6>Users who proceed past checkout entry are highly likely to complete purchase, indicating low friction in later checkout stages.</h6>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="align-right">
            <div class="element">
              <div class="accIcon iconAccTrigger"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accContent" style="">
          <div class="Grid Grid--gutters Grid--full Grid--gutter">
            <div class="Grid-cell">
              <div class="element">
                <h6>Funnel: begin_checkout → add_payment → purchase</h6>
                <h6><span class="fontWeight400"> Web: </span> ~99% step completion</h6>
                <h6><span class="fontWeight400"> Mobile web:</span> ~97–98%</h6>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
